ght I've caused. I'll be sure to haunt elsewhere from now on.\"</p><p>And with that, the ghost vanished into the night, leaving behind a group of bewildered but relieved guests, each with a story to tell about the time they accidentally booked a haunted Airbnb.</p>" });

