nvisible Man melted back into the shadows, his whereabouts once again a mystery. And as the seekers dispersed, each vowing to train harder for next year's event, one thing was certain – the legend of the Invisible Man would continue to grow, a testament to the enduring allure of the unseen.</p>" });

