s own.</p><p>As the sun set over the city, the streets slowly returned to their usual frenetic pace, but the memory of the Giant Snail Races lingered on. For on this day, the slowest and slimiest among us had reigned supreme, reminding us all that sometimes, the most extraordinary things in life happen at a snail's pace.</p>" });

